N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 219.6 - Conflicts with other rules

State Regulations

It is not intended that this Part conflict with or supersede any rules currently in force or subsequently adopted by this department governing specific aspects of the sale or replacement of life insurance or annuities, including but not limited to rules dealing with life insurance cost comparisons and deceptive practices in the sale and replacement of policies.
